7f1528e","tid":49571,"uid":37253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"起碼有兩屆立法會主席<br />\n係同民建聯有關<br />\n<br />\n而主席係普通議員的一倍<br />\n前途美好，人工又好"},{"pid":"98b17cdf55138753136cd6fa40e5e1dc1d6c1551","tid":49571,"uid":40469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:15:16.000Z","msg":"係呀！泛民丶本士丶青政等<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅成員好少做到立法會主席<br />\n<br />\n做到主席，其名字會刻在立法會木牌上<br />\n<br />\n真係有無尚光榮"},{"pid":"a605cf872af28f6302d3dc62d7a71257a2778a0e","tid":49571,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:18:17.000Z","msg":"入去做鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1669c23bb8e9955bfb571fe8f025e0a0ab1c8c","tid":49571,"uid":37253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"立法會主席，人工高<br />\n又光宗耀祖，名字刻在木牌上<br />\n每個議員都可以見到其名字<br />\n<br />\n當然唔係每個黨派成員都有機會做<br />\n<br />\n做到就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c60fca1a813ff112e651cf3f3160100bde37477","tid":49571,"uid":40959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:34:34.000Z","msg":"育乘做咗兩屆立法會主席<br />\n而佢係民建聯<br />\n就算佢唔做主席都經常上電視<br />\n真係好威威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而泛民X派一定冇可能做到主席<br />\n青政成員更加唔使講，連入閘都冇機會"},{"pid":"9d3fbe04e0c627c89770816416e658d1302f177f","tid":49571,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:38:06.000Z","msg":"入淫賤聯全部係雞係屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0747bf70bbdd1f8325ee3c47fadeb8e3ffaa9e","tid":49571,"